{"tid":311351,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"屋邨巴絲互助委員會","createTime":"2017-07-06T14:10:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-07T10:10:58.000Z","uid":64607,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"250b78ed249dd05f7294ad688488795ecbdee828","tid":311351,"uid":64607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T14:10:51.000Z","msg":"我住葵涌，銅鑼灣返工，每日來回兩粒幾鐘。但平時放工仲要衝返家煮晚飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 忽然覺得太辛苦完全無哂自己時間咁。有無巴絲住附近有媽媽愛心飯比我痴餐（我攞兜裝返屋企自己食就得）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 月計著量比返人工食材費你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唉，純綷ff 下，每晚返去到對面屋已經成家開緊餐，我就仲捱緊世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又唔想3餐都出面食..."},{"pid":"76c1ab26a0a9ed19f1e4dfed4722c8eeaef22a6e","tid":311351,"uid":5522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T14:45:45.000Z","msg":"你係絲我煮埋俾你又 點話<br />\nbtw 我記得之前有人上網賣飯盒40-50左右"},{"pid":"6732f58d3fbb056c3fe9ec588a2798a34fd0ceaf","tid":311351,"uid":64607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T15:23:50.000Z","msg":"巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想食個飯姐，都要男女有別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4,50蚊飯盒係住家菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d28ce7078859132f15fdcb356bfba906b14ef85","tid":311351,"uid":64607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T15:27:00.000Z","msg":"最壞打算每日大家樂宵夜，狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但勝在算平，30幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"951d978b46b2585e0b299f9e3a0000800433c592","tid":311351,"uid":73671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T15:43:11.000Z","msg":"住葵涌邊到？<br />\n<br />\n平時收工返到樓下<br />\n如果大快活都閂門就仆街<br />\n真係唯有去ok 食叮叮"},{"pid":"adbd7f4375242dd7719c9695728326b3a168f56e","tid":311351,"uid"